00:19:26.830 --> 00:19:27.830
being.

00:19:27.830 --> 00:19:33.519
Now when we forget this, we are only worried
about the physical side of it.

00:19:33.519 --> 00:19:40.779
And when our physical side is in trouble,
we want to do everything under the sun; but

00:19:40.779 --> 00:19:44.539
we do not know by doing that we are spoiling
our emotional side.

00:19:44.539 --> 00:19:50.879
