very dangerous, that medicines, which reduce

00:19:50.879 --> 00:19:56.929
the anti-bodies in the body, can lead you
to madness, ultimately.

00:19:56.929 --> 00:20:01.660
First they give you giddiness, must you sleep
a lot, and after that too much sleeping, too

00:20:01.660 --> 00:20:04.759
much of these medicines, can cause madness.

00:20:04.759 --> 00:20:09.419
Because you are thrown into the left side
and you can be attacked and you can become

00:20:09.419 --> 00:20:10.889
a mad person.

00:20:10.889 --> 00:20:16.789
So these medicines are so dangerous that people
without understanding the complete nature

00:20:16.789 --> 00:20:20.279
of man just try to treat part of it.

00:20:20.279 --> 00:20:27.529
In Sahaja Yoga we, as he said, I do not take
any medicines, My ….

00:20:27.529 --> 00:20:32.619
as Kabira has said, “I do not take any medicines,
for me Parabrahma is the one who is my Vaidya,

00:20:32.619 --> 00:20:33.669
He treats me”.

00:20:33.669 --> 00:20:39.820
And is a fact, now the time has come to prove
what Kabira has said, what Nanaka has said,

00:20:39.820 --> 00:20:43.389
what Adi Shankaracharya has said, what Christ
has said.

00:20:43.389 --> 00:20:47.619
There is no need to take medicine to cure
this centre.

00:20:47.619 --> 00:20:51.139
We spoil this centre by other means also.

00:20:51.139 --> 00:20:53.320
For example, if you…

00:20:53.320 --> 00:20:56.409
there can be very simple reasons for spoiling
it.

00:20:56.409 --> 00:20:59.279
You take your bath with hot water.

00:20:59.279 --> 00:21:04.559
Normally to take a hot bath – a hot bath
is all right, but that should be done in the

00:21:04.559 --> 00:21:06.909
night when you don’t go out at all.

00:21:06.909 --> 00:21:10.760
Then you sleep off, you are in the room and
there cannot be a problem.

00:21:10.760 --> 00:21:15.960
But I’ve seen in England most of the Indians
who come and see Me have got trouble with

00:21:15.960 --> 00:21:16.960
their lungs.

00:21:16.960 --> 00:21:21.840
They have a problem with their lungs and sometimes
they get lung cancer very easily.

00:21:21.840 --> 00:21:25.690
And what I found out that they take a very
hot bath like English people.

00:21:25.690 --> 00:21:28.639
Actually English people take seldom their
baths.

00:21:28.639 --> 00:21:34.989
So [She laughs, general laughter] and it is
very common to see in English homes sixty

00:21:34.989 --> 00:21:38.009
bedrooms with a bath, you see.

00:21:38.009 --> 00:21:40.639
Because they don’t require it much.

00:21:40.639 --> 00:21:42.460
But even if they have to take, they take it
in the night.

00:21:42.460 --> 00:21:45.739
[Laughter] They don’t take it early in the
morning like Indians do.

00:21:45.739 --> 00:21:49.809
You see, you have to live in England the way
English are – and not that, you cannot live

00:21:49.809 --> 00:21:57.340
like that, is a bit too much [laughter] – but
still you can sometimes understand that if

00:21:57.340 --> 00:22:02.460
you have to take the bath early in the morning,
and then go to office, you are definite to

00:22:02.460 --> 00:22:07.809
catch this centre or a centre next to that
which is called as right heart in our Sahaja

00:22:07.809 --> 00:22:09.610
Yoga language.

00:22:09.610 --> 00:22:16.529
Now this center heart is caught, or the right
heart is caught, because you suddenly expose

00:22:16.529 --> 00:22:19.489
yourself to cold weather.

00:22:19.489 --> 00:22:24.220
In the same way in Delhi you may catch it,
that you just have your hot bath and get out

00:22:24.220 --> 00:22:26.039
into the cold.

00:22:26.039 --> 00:22:33.460
Now best thing is that you take your hot bath
always, and then allow the water to be mixed

00:22:33.460 --> 00:22:40.889
with cold water, make the tap run and then
you take your bath, end up with cool water.

00:22:40.889 --> 00:22:45.059
You’ll be amazed you will never catch cold.

00:22:45.059 --> 00:22:47.740
Is a very simple thing to do.

00:22:47.740 --> 00:22:51.320
Once you practice this, you will never catch
cold.

00:22:51.320 --> 00:22:58.600
I have seen people living very near Himalayas
where it’s absolutely very, very cold twelve

00:22:58.600 --> 00:22:59.600
months.

00:22:59.600 --> 00:23:08.450
They always take their baths early in the
morning sitting outside with cold water.

00:23:08.450 --> 00:23:11.080
They never take bath with hot water.

00:23:11.080 --> 00:23:14.279
They never have hot water to take their bath.

00:23:14.279 --> 00:23:19.940
And I’ve not seen any person suffering from
this cold in the hills.

00:23:19.940 --> 00:23:24.340
They keep very good health as far as the cold
is concerned despite the fact it is very cold.

00:23:24.340 --> 00:23:30.039
It’s a matter of little habit, if the sahaj
yogis who are realized souls, if they practice

00:23:30.039 --> 00:23:34.950
this, I tell you all your Vishuddhis which
are so horribly caught up will be all right

00:23:34.950 --> 00:23:38.970
and I will have less trouble [laughter, She
laughs].

00:23:38.970 --> 00:23:43.710
Because today I was clearing everybody’s
Vishuddhi there.

00:23:43.710 --> 00:23:49.279
Now this right-side heart is caught up, is
most surprising that it is caught up, because

00:23:49.279 --> 00:23:56.190
it is the, it is bestowed upon by the deity
of Shri Rama.

00:23:56.190 --> 00:23:58.460
Shri Rama is the Father deity.

00:23:58.460 --> 00:24:08.359
He is the Father, he is the Father king and
he is the Father of this world, is the Father

00:24:08.359 --> 00:24:09.359
head.

00:24:09.359 --> 00:24:12.840
Supposing you are a bad father, you will catch
this.

00:24:12.840 --> 00:24:18.049
Ultimately, with this center you always get
asthma, always.

00:24:18.049 --> 00:24:23.090
All asthma patients who have come to Me have
been cured – so far.

00:24:23.090 --> 00:24:27.889
I have cured most of the ailments of right
heart.

00:24:27.889 --> 00:24:33.520
There is another cause of this is, supposing
somebody’s father is dead in early years,

00:24:33.520 --> 00:24:39.969
very early years when the child was not yet
properly settled down, or he died at a time

00:24:39.969 --> 00:24:45.739
with an accident or may be with a worry about
the child.

00:24:45.739 --> 00:24:46.759
Then he haunts the child.

00:24:46.759 --> 00:24:48.129
This is true.

00:24:48.129 --> 00:24:54.950
At that time, if you just tell your father
that “I’m all right, don’t worry, you

00:24:54.950 --> 00:25:00.799
take your birth, I’ll be all right”, you’ll
be amazed, this asthma can go.

00:25:00.799 --> 00:25:07.879
There was a governor of Kashmir, who was a
very, very respectable man and we had gone

00:25:07.879 --> 00:25:11.519
to him as state guests.

00:25:11.519 --> 00:25:18.010
